articles.title: Tenacious D Australia Concert Postponed After Trump Shooting Joke, As Local Politician Calls for Band to be Deported - Hollywood Reporter
articles.description: The comedy rock duo, comprising Jack Black and Kyle Gass, made a bad taste joke about the former president at a gig in Sydney on Sunday and postponed a concert in Newcastle at short notice.
